snippet.textDisplay:
I have listened to many asma ul hasna recited by others but this one is unique. The body language is so amazing that it seems like he is standing Infront of Allah s.w.t and reciting from heart. Reciting like one friend is standing in front of other, bear footed, pleasing him by praising. Atif give the feeling that he is very happy, passionate and in love and in deep joy. In short one Malang or Turkish Sufi is reciting asma ul husna. 

Allah s.w.t can better judge whether this act was fake and for marketing and promotion purpose but It feels to me that Allah s.w.t is very merciful that may be he will make this recitation purpose of forgiveness on the day of judgement for him.
